'''寶永地震'''（{{Lang-ja|宝永地震}}）是[[日本|日本]]有记录以来最強烈的[[地震|地震]]<ref name="IISEE">{{cite web|url=http://iisee.kenken.go.jp/utsu/index_eng.html|title=Catalog of Damaging Earthquakes in the World (Through 2007)|last=IISEE|accessdate=2009-12-23|archive-date=2010-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100306180217/http://iisee.kenken.go.jp/utsu/index_eng.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kotobank">{{Cite web|title=宝永地震とは|url=https://kotobank.jp/word/%E5%AE%9D%E6%B0%B8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87-156276|access-date=2022-03-26|last=|first=|work=コトバンク|language=ja}}</ref>，在[[江戶時代|江戶時代]]的[[1707年|1707年]]10月28日（[[寶永|寶永]]4年10月初4日）於當地時間在下午2點發生<ref>{{Cite web|title=宝永地震（宝永4年10月4日）|url=https://typhoon.yahoo.co.jp/weather/calendar/281/|access-date=2022-03-26|work=Yahoo!天気・災害|publisher=災害カレンダー|language=ja}}</ref><ref>[https://www.bousai.go.jp/kyoiku/kyokun/kyoukunnokeishou/rep/1707_houeijishin/pdf/05_chap01.pdf 宝永地震の地震像] - 内閣府防災情報</ref>，[[震央|震央]]大約位於在今日的[[和歌山縣|和歌山縣]]南端以南30公里處外海。該次地震讓整個[[本州|本州]]西南部、[[四國|四國]]以及[[九州_(日本)|九州]]東南部地區都造成了中度到嚴重等不同等級的損害<ref name="Miyazawa">{{cite web |url=http://www.dpri.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dat/nenpo/no48/48c0/a48c0p13.pdf |title=Historical maximum seismic intensity maps in Japan from 1586 to 2004: construction of database and application |last1=Miyazawa |first1=M. |author2=Mori J. |date=2005 |work=Annal of Disas.Prev.Res.Inst., Kyoto Univ. 48C |accessdate=2010-01-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722072314/https://www.dpri.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dat/nenpo/no48/48c0/a48c0p13.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-22 }}</ref>。因為強烈的主震以及所引發破壞性的巨大[[海嘯|海嘯]]，導致了至少有5,000人到20,000人罹難與大量財產建築物的損失<ref name="Ando">{{cite web |url=http://www.gsj.jp/GDB/openfile/files/no0484/PDF/06_Ando/Ando_ppt.pdf |title=Groundwater and Coastal Phenomena Preceding the 1944 Tsunami (Tonankai Earthquake) |last1=Ando |first1=M. |date=2006 |accessdate=2010-01-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720001529/http://www.gsj.jp/GDB/openfile/files/no0484/PDF/06_Ando/Ando_ppt.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-20 }}</ref>，該次地震也被認為與事發大約49天之後的[[寶永大噴發|寶永大噴發]]有關係<ref name="Hill">{{cite journal|last1=Hill|first1=D.P.|author2=Pollitz F.|author3=Newhall C.|date=2002|title=Earthquake-Volcano Interactions|journal=Physica Today|issue=November|pages=41–47|url=http://earthobservatory.sg/downloads/publications/chrisnewhall/83-Eq-volcano-interactions-Hill-etal-Phys-Today-2002.pdf|accessdate=2010-01-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815111840/http://earthobservatory.sg/downloads/publications/chrisnewhall/83-Eq-volcano-interactions-Hill-etal-Phys-Today-2002.pdf|archivedate=2011-08-15}}</ref>。

== 破壞 ==
總共有60,000棟房屋在該次地震中都遭到了倒塌，其中有20,000棟房屋都被巨大海嘯給沖走，罹難人數有5,000人到20,000人之間，在[[靜岡縣|靜岡縣]]的山區在該次地震之後就發生了至少有一起的大型[[山崩|山體滑坡]]事件<ref name="sidle">{{cite web|url=http://www.iuss.org/Hydropedology/Hydropedology%20june_2008.pdf|title=Triggering Mechanisms of Landslides and Debris Flows and Their Linkages: Hydrogeomorphic and Hydropedologic Influences|last1=Sidle|first1=R.C.|author2=Imaizumi F.|date=2008|work=1st International Conference on Hydropedology Highlights of Presentations|accessdate=2010-01-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727075518/http://www.iuss.org/Hydropedology/Hydropedology%20june_2008.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-27}}</ref>。這起山體滑坡的規模為日本有紀錄以來前三大之一，涵蓋面積大約為1.8平方公里，土方總共約為1.20億立方公尺，也被稱作為「大谷滑坡」<ref name="Ohya">{{cite web|url=http://www.nilim.go.jp/lab/bcg/siryou/tnn/tnn0277pdf/ks0277008.pdf|title=Case 2: Oya Hillside work|accessdate=30 January 2010|archive-date=2013-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121130435/http://www.nilim.go.jp/lab/bcg/siryou/tnn/tnn0277pdf/ks0277008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[奈良縣|奈良縣]]的盆地也發生了[[土壤液化|土壤液化]]<ref name="Nakanashi">{{cite journal |last=Nakanashi |first=I. |date=1999 |title=Liquefaction Caused by the 1707 Hoei Earthquake as Observed in the Nara Basin, Central Japan |journal=Disaster Prevention Research Institute Annuals, Kyoto University |volume=42 |issue=B1 |pages=125–127 |url=http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200005/000020000500A0102130.php |accessdate=2010-01-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225235238/http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200005/000020000500A0102130.php |archivedate=2012-02-25 }}</ref>。

該次地震也引發了浪高高度為25.7公尺的巨大海嘯。在[[高知縣|高知縣]]的西南海岸在地震之後的引發巨大海嘯上升到高度為7.7公尺，其中有一些部分的地區高度甚至都超過有10公尺到15公尺<ref name="Hatori">{{cite journal|last=Hatori|first=T.|date=1981|title=Field investigations of the Nankaido Tsunamis in 1707 and 1854 along the South-west coast of Shikoku|journal=Bulletin Earthquake Research Institute|volume=56|pages=547–570|language=ja, en|url=http://repository.dl.itc.u-tokyo.ac.jp/dspace/bitstream/2261/12817/1/ji0563006.pdf|accessdate=2009-12-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006004423/http://repository.dl.itc.u-tokyo.ac.jp/dspace/bitstream/2261/12817/1/ji0563006.pdf|archivedate=2011-10-06}}</ref>。

